title: Extra rentable storage on-site, Balcony or patio, Relaxing covered spa
posting_body: ['Welcome to Pleasanton Glen Apartment Homes!', "One look at our spacious floor plans and it's easy to see how Pleasanton Glen is different from other apartments for rent in Pleasanton, CA.", 'With a variety of floor plans to choose from, we’re certain there’s one that’s just right for you.', 'Browse our one, two and three bedroom floor plans.', 'The living spaces at Pleasanton Glen are thoughtfully designed for comfort and convenience in mind, and are stylishly appointed with the kind of premium materials and finishes.', '- Three sparkling pools with sun decks', '- Relaxing covered spa', '- Outdoor lounge area', '- Fully equipped fitness center', '- Beautiful courtyards with mature landscaping', '- Assigned covered parking', '- Extra rentable storage on-site', '- 24-hour laundry center', '- On-site friendly and professional management and maintenance team', '- Blocks from historical Downtown', '- Easy access to Bart, ACE Train, I-680 and I-580', '- Near major Tri-Valley employment centers, shopping, dining & entertainment', '- Award winning Pleasanton school district', '- 24-Hour parcel locker room', '- Many options to pay rent including, credit card, on-line and ACH', '- Resident referral program', '- Granite countertops in kitchen & bathrooms', '- Designer window coverings', '- Balcony or patio', '- Ice maker', '- Full kitchen Whirlpool stainless steel appliance package', '- High-speed internet access', '- Pool, courtyard and creek views', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing is subject to change.', 'Call for details.']
